ğŸ“Œ Why This Structure Is Good

Package	Purpose

app	Application entry point
ui	Swing UI classes only
service	Business logic (hash generation)
model	Data objects (results, DTOs)
util	Common utilities
constants	Algorithms, static values


ğŸ‘‰ This is close to MVC, but lightweight and pure Java


